PN,39701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FVetting checks were found to be out of
OL,8,Fdate for around one in 10 public
OL,9,Fsector workers in young offender
OL,10,Finstitutions, according to a review
OL,11,Fsparked by a scandal which saw
OL,12,Fhundreds of young inmates abused at a
OL,13,Fdetention centre in County Durham
OL,14,Facross three decades.
OL,16,FThe outdated Disclosure and Barring
OL,17,FService (DBS) checks at facilities
OL,18,Facross the country represent a
OL,19,F"significant governance risk",
OL,20,FEngland's chief social worker for
OL,21,Fchildren and families said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHer review, into sites in England and
OL,8,FWales and published on Tuesday, came
OL,9,Fafter an inquiry last year concluded
OL,10,Fsuccessive wardens at Medomsley
OL,11,FDetention Centre were either complicit
OL,12,For incompetent regarding physical and
OL,13,Fsexual abuse there.
OL,15,FThat report by the Prisons and
OL,16,FProbation Ombudsman found staff were
OL,17,Fleft to decide how the centre ` which
OL,18,Fwas open from 1961 to 1987 ` operated.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt also found inmates, referred to as
OL,8,F"trainees" at the centre designed to
OL,9,Fgive a few weeks of military style
OL,10,Fdiscipline, were physically abused
OL,11,Ffrom the moment they arrived. They
OL,12,Fwere normally aged between 17 and 21.
OL,14,FWhen it was published in November, the
OL,15,FGovernment apologised to victims and
OL,16,Fsurvivors on behalf of the current and
OL,17,Fpast governments, and ordered a review
OL,18,Finto youth custody facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIn her review, published on Tuesday (7
OL,8,FJuly), chief social worker Isabelle
OL,9,FTrowler, said there was a "significant
OL,10,Fgovernance risk" from the fact
OL,11,Fapproximately 10% of public sector
OL,12,FYoung Offender Institution (YOI) staff
OL,13,Fhad out-of-date Disclosure and Barring
OL,14,FService (DBS) checks as of February
OL,15,Fthis year.
OL,17,FHer report also said almost a fifth
OL,18,F(18%) of staff in prisons where there
OL,19,Fare mother and baby units were found
OL,20,Fto have out-of-date DBS checks.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FShe also concluded there were
OL,8,F"significant investigative weaknesses"
OL,9,Fin safeguarding including "examples of
OL,10,Fpremature and/or inadvertent
OL,11,Fdisclosure of concerns to alleged
OL,12,Fperpetrators" and a failure to
OL,13,Finterview alleged victims and
OL,14,Fperpetrators.
OL,16,FShe said: "This hampers, or prevents,
OL,17,Fdisciplinary action, criminal
OL,18,Finvestigations and charges and, most
OL,19,Fimportantly, the ability to protect
OL,20,Fchildren from harm."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@fO]qD@[OUtD@MO]xD@KOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHer review looked at the youth
OL,8,Fcustodial estate which includes Young
OL,9,FOffender Institutions, Secure Training
OL,10,FCentres and Secure Children's Homes,
OL,11,Fand she described the difference in
OL,12,Fthe quality of care and resources
OL,13,Favailable across settings as "stark".
OL,15,FIn the 12 months leading up to her
OL,16,Freview, Ms Trowler said there were
OL,17,Fapproximately 420 children in custody
OL,18,Fin England and Wales, describing many
OL,19,Fof them as "extremely vulnerable, with
OL,20,Fhigh level and complex needs".
OL,26,@uD@^OUuD@dO]{D@LOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FShe said many will have already
OL,8,Fexperienced "intense trauma, adversity
OL,9,Fand difficulty in their lives" and
OL,10,Fhave also "been accused or convicted
OL,11,Fof the most serious offences, causing
OL,12,Fsignificant harm and pain to others".
OL,14,FShe added: "We must hold these two
OL,15,Frealities together at the same time."
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@^O]rD@KOUtD@dO]vD@LOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FMs Trowler's review made 34
OL,8,Frecommendations, all of which the
OL,9,FGovernment said it had accepted in
OL,10,Fprinciple, as it promised strengthened
OL,11,Fvetting of staff and better access to
OL,12,Fsocial workers.
OL,14,FThe recommendations included ensuring
OL,15,Fall outstanding enhanced DBS checks
OL,16,F"are completed without further delay"
OL,17,Fand for enhanced checks to take place
OL,18,Fevery three years across all youth
OL,19,Fcustody sites.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FShe also said all children in youth
OL,8,Fcustody should be considered "looked
OL,9,Fafter" by the home local authority,
OL,10,F"to maximise opportunities for
OL,11,Fsafeguarding in custody, the
OL,12,Ffacilitation and strengthening of
OL,13,Ffamily relationships and resettlement
OL,14,Fplans".
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@FO]rD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Justice committed to
OL,8,Fstronger staff training, tougher
OL,9,Fvetting for anyone working directly
OL,10,Fwith children and better safeguarding
OL,11,Fprocesses "to ensure all allegations
OL,12,Fof wrongdoing are investigated
OL,13,Frobustly and acted upon swiftly".
OL,15,FEvery site in the youth custody estate
OL,16,Fwill be required to have access to a
OL,17,Fdedicated social worker with extensive
OL,18,Fchild protection expertise, to ensure
OL,19,Fconcerns cannot be ignored or handled
OL,20,Fonly internally, the department said.
OL,26,@sD@KOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FFulfilling the recommendation on all
OL,8,Fchildren in custody being given the
OL,9,Fsame formal protections as children in
OL,10,Fcare will require new legislation, the
OL,11,FMoJ said, but added that social
OL,12,Fworkers will, in the meantime,
OL,13,Fproactively check in with children
OL,14,F"and provide a safe, private space to
OL,15,Fraise any concerns".
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FYouth Justice minister Jake Richards,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The abuse that took place at
OL,9,FMedomsley is a national scandal and it
OL,10,Fis right that the Government has
OL,11,Fapologised. While we cannot undo the
OL,12,Fpain suffered by victims, we can make
OL,13,Fsure nothing like it ever happens
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"That is why we're taking forward all
OL,8,F34 recommendations, including
OL,9,Findependent oversight of every abuse
OL,10,Fallegation, giving every child in
OL,11,Fcustody access to a social worker, and
OL,12,Fstrengthening staff vetting to keep
OL,13,Fchildren in custody safe.
OL,15,F"A system that fails to protect
OL,16,Fchildren in custody creates more
OL,17,Fvictims, not fewer. These reforms are
OL,18,Fabout breaking that cycle."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt is understood hundreds, if not
OL,8,Fthousands, of young inmates were
OL,9,Fvictims of systematic abuse at
OL,10,FMedomsley Detention Centre.
OL,12,FPart of last year's inquiry focused on
OL,13,Fofficer Neville Husband, who was
OL,14,Fdescribed "as possibly the most
OL,15,Fprolific sex offender in British
OL,16,Fhistory".
OL,26,@vD@KOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHusband was thought to have groomed
OL,8,Fand attacked hundreds of trainees in
OL,9,FMedomsley's kitchens. He was convicted
OL,10,Fof sexual assault and was jailed in
OL,11,F2003 and again in 2005. He died in
OL,12,F2010.
OL,14,FMore than 2,000 former inmates came
OL,15,Fforward to give their testimony to
OL,16,FOperation Seabrook, a police
OL,17,Finvestigation which led to five
OL,18,Fretired officers being convicted of
OL,19,Fabuse in 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FMs Trowler, said: "While there have
OL,8,Fbeen improvements in recent years, the
OL,9,Fevidence is unequivocal: more must be
OL,10,Fdone to ensure every child in custody
OL,11,Fis safe, listened to and treated with
OL,12,Fdignity.
OL,14,F"It is now incumbent upon the
OL,15,FGovernment and, in turn, HMPPS and
OL,16,Flocal authority children's services to
OL,17,Fmake change happen.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Meeting children currently in custody
OL,8,Fand hearing directly about their
OL,9,Fexperiences has been both a privilege
OL,10,Fand a profound responsibility. This
OL,11,Fexperience, and the stories children
OL,12,Fshared, will likely stay with me
OL,13,Fforever. We owe it to them, and to
OL,14,Fthose who suffered in the past, to
OL,15,Fensure that the findings of this
OL,16,Freview lead to meaningful and lasting
OL,17,Fchange."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman Adrian
OL,8,FUsher, said: "My investigative report
OL,9,Frevealed the full scale and horror of
OL,10,Fwhat happened to thousands of victims
OL,11,Fat Medomsley Detention Centre. The
OL,12,Fabuse that took place there was a
OL,13,Fprofound failure by those responsible
OL,14,Ffor the care and protection of
OL,15,Fchildren and young people in custody.
OL,26,@pD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"I welcome the Government's commitment
OL,8,Fto implementing the recommendations
OL,9,Ffrom the Trowler Review and
OL,10,Fstrengthening safeguarding across the
OL,11,Fyouth estate. While nothing can undo
OL,12,Fthe harm suffered by victims, these
OL,13,Freforms are an important step towards
OL,14,Fensuring lessons of the past are
OL,15,Flearned and that children in custody
OL,16,Fare better protected in the future."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783714848
OL,3,COutdated vetting poses 'significant
OL,4,Cgovernance risk' youth custody review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe MoJ said that as health, social
OL,8,Fcare and education are devolved in
OL,9,FWales, the majority of the actions set
OL,10,Fout in the Government response relate
OL,11,Fto England.
OL,13,FWho to contact if you are looking for
OL,14,Fhelp and support
OL,16,FThe Meadows Sexual Assault Referral
OL,17,FCentre provides free, confidential
OL,18,Fhealthcare andcompassionate support to
OL,19,Fpeople who have experienced rape or
OL,20,Fsexual assault. Call 0330 223 0099 or
OL,21,Fvisit www.themeadowsdurham.org.uk
